  <h1>variidian/about <img src="/images/persona1.png" alt="a tiny persona i drew"></h1>
  <p>heyo! I go by variidian/shurui (she/her) and am a 14 y/o from Sydney, Australia :p</p>
  
  <img src="/images/shaw_art.png" alt="shaw art">

  <p>Apart from coding, things i like include:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>- videogames! - minecraft, pokemon, botw, hollowknight and peak come to mind- haven't played much of the last two though :pensive-wobble:</li>
    <li>- plushies - imo you can never have too many - blahaj. blhaj. bhalaj. </li>
    <li>- Books >> movies - sci-fi and fantasy! - off the top of my head i do remember enjoying <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wings_of_Fire_(novel_series)">Wings of Fire</a> and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Warriors_(novel_series)">Warrior Cats</a> back in 2022 :] wow its been a few years.</li>
